[quote=&quot;TriangleGames&quot;:ek8shumc]I just upgraded from 5.3 to 5.4 beta, and I can't open any of my games to play OR edit.[/quote:ek8shumc]

The problem is with the program, but you can fix it by editing your game's coding. I had to fix it myself, and it's really simple. Just open your game's .aslx file in a text editor and at the very top, where it says 
[code:ek8shumc]&lt;asl version=&quot;530&quot;&gt;[/code:ek8shumc]
Change it to
[code:ek8shumc]&lt;asl version=&quot;540&quot;&gt;[/code:ek8shumc]

